  "title": "Senior Electrical Engineer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Role & Responsibilities :</strong></p><p>•\tLeading electrical design including calculations (e.g. voltage drop, short circuit current), SLD, Schematic</p><p>•\tdrawings, and other technical documentation and reports.</p><p>•\tCoordination, overseeing site installation, testing, and commissioning, and ensuring compliance with safety regulations and project specifications.</p><p>•\tLiaise with consultants, subcontractors, suppliers and other engineering disciplines (ACMV, BMS, etc.) to resolve technical issues and ensure project objects are met.</p><p>•\tConduct site inspection, review method statement and risk assessment, and ensure all works comply with approved specifications.</p><p>•\tBIM experiences will be added advantage.</p><p>•\tAny other tasks assigned by the line manager.</p><p></p>",
